# Editorial Design System

Read `docs/EDITORIAL_DESIGN_SYSTEM.md` before any UI change.

## Non-negotiables

- Use `Typography*` components only — never custom font sizes
- Helvetica ~95%, Quartz ~5% (hero + quote only, max 6 words)
- All Helvetica titles uppercase via components
- Spacing on 8px grid (`editorialSpace` / `editorial.stack`)
- Compose sections with `EditorialSection` — do not repeat identical layouts
- Typography is composition, not decoration

## Components

`TypographyLabel` · `TypographyHero` · `TypographySection` · `TypographyCard` · `TypographyLead` · `TypographyBody` · `TypographyMeta` · `TypographyButton` · `TypographyQuote`

## Visual DNA

Swiss typography · editorial grids · museum catalogue · art publication — not a template portfolio.
